62template <typename T>
63using ResourceErrorOr = Expected<T, ResourceError>;
64
65enum class CachePolicy : uint8_t;
66enum class ImageLoading : uint8_t { Immediate, DeferredUntilVisible };
67
68// The CachedResourceLoader provides a per-context interface to the MemoryCache
69// and enforces a bunch of security checks and rules for resource revalidation.
70// Its lifetime is roughly per-DocumentLoader, in that it is generally created
71// in the DocumentLoader constructor and loses its ability to generate network
72// requests when the DocumentLoader is destroyed. Documents also hold a
73// RefPtr<CachedResourceLoader> for their lifetime (and will create one if they
74// are initialized without a Frame), so a Document can keep a CachedResourceLoader
75// alive past detach if scripts still reference the Document.
76class CachedResourceLoader : public RefCounted<CachedResourceLoader> {
77 WTF_MAKE_NONCOPYABLE(CachedResourceLoader); WTF_MAKE_FAST_ALLOCATED;
78friend class ImageLoader;
79friend class ResourceCacheValidationSuppressor;
80
81public:
82 static Ref<CachedResourceLoader> create(DocumentLoader* documentLoader) { return adoptRef(*new CachedResourceLoader(documentLoader)); }
83 ~CachedResourceLoader();
84
85 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedImage>> requestImage(CachedResourceRequest&&, ImageLoading = ImageLoading::Immediate);
86 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedCSSStyleSheet>> requestCSSStyleSheet(CachedResourceRequest&&);
87 CachedResourceHandle<CachedCSSStyleSheet> requestUserCSSStyleSheet(Page&, CachedResourceRequest&&);
88 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedScript>> requestScript(CachedResourceRequest&&);
89 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedFont>> requestFont(CachedResourceRequest&&, bool isSVG);
90 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestMedia(CachedResourceRequest&&);
91 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestIcon(CachedResourceRequest&&);
92 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestBeaconResource(CachedResourceRequest&&);
93 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestPingResource(CachedResourceRequest&&);
94 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestMainResource(CachedResourceRequest&&);
95 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedSVGDocument>> requestSVGDocument(CachedResourceRequest&&);
96#if ENABLE(XSLT)
97 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedXSLStyleSheet>> requestXSLStyleSheet(CachedResourceRequest&&);
98#endif
99 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource>> requestLinkResource(CachedResource::Type, CachedResourceRequest&&);
100#if ENABLE(VIDEO)
101 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedTextTrack>> requestTextTrack(CachedResourceRequest&&);
102#endif
103#if ENABLE(APPLICATION_MANIFEST)
104 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedApplicationManifest>> requestApplicationManifest(CachedResourceRequest&&);
105#endif
106#if ENABLE(MODEL_ELEMENT)
107 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestModelResource(CachedResourceRequest&&);
108#endif
109
110 // Called to load Web Worker main script, Service Worker main script, importScripts(), XHR,
111 // EventSource, Fetch, and App Cache.
112 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedRawResource>> requestRawResource(CachedResourceRequest&&);
113
114 // Logs an access denied message to the console for the specified URL.
115 void printAccessDeniedMessage(const URL& url) const;

117 CachedResource* cachedResource(const String& url) const;
118 CachedResource* cachedResource(const URL& url) const;

123 void notifyFinished(const CachedResource&);
124 Vector<Ref<SVGImage>> allCachedSVGImages() const;

132 bool shouldDeferImageLoad(const URL&) const;
133 bool shouldPerformImageLoad(const URL&) const;
134
135 CachePolicy cachePolicy(CachedResource::Type, const URL&) const;
136
137 Frame* frame() const; // Can be null
138 Document* document() const { return m_document.get(); } // Can be null
139 void setDocument(Document* document) { m_document = makeWeakPtr(document); }
140 void clearDocumentLoader() { m_documentLoader = nullptr; }
141
142 void loadDone(LoadCompletionType, bool shouldPerformPostLoadActions = true);
143
144 WEBCORE_EXPORT void garbageCollectDocumentResources();
145
146 void incrementRequestCount(const CachedResource&);
147 void decrementRequestCount(const CachedResource&);
148 int requestCount() const { return m_requestCount; }
149
150 WEBCORE_EXPORT bool isPreloaded(const String& urlString) const;
151 enum class ClearPreloadsMode { ClearSpeculativePreloads, ClearAllPreloads };
152 void clearPreloads(ClearPreloadsMode);
153 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource>> preload(CachedResource::Type, CachedResourceRequest&&);
154 void printPreloadStats();
155 void warnUnusedPreloads();
156 void stopUnusedPreloadsTimer();
157
158 bool updateRequestAfterRedirection(CachedResource::Type, ResourceRequest&, const ResourceLoaderOptions&);
159 bool allowedByContentSecurityPolicy(CachedResource::Type, const URL&, const ResourceLoaderOptions&, ContentSecurityPolicy::RedirectResponseReceived) const;
160
161 static const ResourceLoaderOptions& defaultCachedResourceOptions();
162
163 void documentDidFinishLoadEvent();
164
165 ResourceTimingInformation& resourceTimingInformation() { return m_resourceTimingInfo; }
166
167 KeepaliveRequestTracker& keepaliveRequestTracker() { return m_keepaliveRequestTracker; }
168
169 Vector<CachedResource*> visibleResourcesToPrioritize();
170
171private:
172 explicit CachedResourceLoader(DocumentLoader*);
173
174 enum class ForPreload { Yes, No };
175
176 ResourceErrorOr<CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource>> requestResource(CachedResource::Type, CachedResourceRequest&&, ForPreload = ForPreload::No, ImageLoading = ImageLoading::Immediate);
177 CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource> revalidateResource(CachedResourceRequest&&, CachedResource&);
178 CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource> loadResource(CachedResource::Type, PAL::SessionID, CachedResourceRequest&&, const CookieJar&, const Settings&);
179
180 void prepareFetch(CachedResource::Type, CachedResourceRequest&);
181 void updateHTTPRequestHeaders(FrameLoader&, CachedResource::Type, CachedResourceRequest&);
182
183 bool canRequest(CachedResource::Type, const URL&, const ResourceLoaderOptions&, ForPreload);
184
185 enum RevalidationPolicy { Use, Revalidate, Reload, Load };
186 RevalidationPolicy determineRevalidationPolicy(CachedResource::Type, CachedResourceRequest&, CachedResource* existingResource, ForPreload, ImageLoading) const;
187
188 bool shouldUpdateCachedResourceWithCurrentRequest(const CachedResource&, const CachedResourceRequest&);
189 CachedResourceHandle<CachedResource> updateCachedResourceWithCurrentRequest(const CachedResource&, CachedResourceRequest&&, PAL::SessionID, const CookieJar&, const Settings&);
190
191 bool shouldContinueAfterNotifyingLoadedFromMemoryCache(const CachedResourceRequest&, CachedResource&, ResourceError&);
192 bool checkInsecureContent(CachedResource::Type, const URL&) const;
193
194 void performPostLoadActions();
195
196 ImageLoading clientDefersImage(const URL&) const;
197 void reloadImagesIfNotDeferred();
198
199 bool canRequestAfterRedirection(CachedResource::Type, const URL&, const ResourceLoaderOptions&) const;
200 bool canRequestInContentDispositionAttachmentSandbox(CachedResource::Type, const URL&) const;
201
202 HashSet<String> m_validatedURLs;
203 HashSet<String> m_cachedSVGImagesURLs;
204 mutable DocumentResourceMap m_documentResources;
205 WeakPtr<Document> m_document;
206 DocumentLoader* m_documentLoader;
207
208 int m_requestCount { 0 };
209
210 std::unique_ptr<ListHashSet<CachedResource*>> m_preloads;
211 Timer m_unusedPreloadsTimer;
212
213 Timer m_garbageCollectDocumentResourcesTimer;
214
215 ResourceTimingInformation m_resourceTimingInfo;
216 KeepaliveRequestTracker m_keepaliveRequestTracker;
217
218 bool m_autoLoadImages { true };
219 bool m_imagesEnabled { true };
220 bool m_allowStaleResources { false };
221};
222
223class ResourceCacheValidationSuppressor {
224 WTF_MAKE_NONCOPYABLE(ResourceCacheValidationSuppressor);
225 WTF_MAKE_FAST_ALLOCATED;
226public:
227 ResourceCacheValidationSuppressor(CachedResourceLoader& loader)
228 : m_loader(loader)
229 , m_previousState(m_loader.m_allowStaleResources)
230 {
231 m_loader.m_allowStaleResources = true;
232 }
233 ~ResourceCacheValidationSuppressor()
234 {
235 m_loader.m_allowStaleResources = m_previousState;
236 }
237private:
238 CachedResourceLoader& m_loader;
239 bool m_previousState;
240};
